	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎哎、<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay40 />
我们不都是女孩子嘛，<delay20 />
偶尔也来聊一点女生话题呀！<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你说女生话题<tag a="110" b="0" />是吗？</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对呀！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay40 />
比如说时尚呀<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或者是恋爱的事情！
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～<delay20 />这样吧，<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你有没有什么
可以推荐的潮牌<delay8 /><20_2 arg="4" />～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好意思，<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay40 />
我在时尚这方面，<delay8 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />实在是没什么讲究<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～<20_2 arg="3" /><delay8 />太无趣了啦～<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那这样吧，<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有什么比较在意的事情吗？<20_2 arg="4" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有一件很在意的事情！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一言以蔽之的话，<delay8 />
就是“蟑螂的可能性”！<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<20_2 arg="8" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家都很讨厌蟑螂对吧！<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_3 arg="4" /><delay20 />
我也很害怕！！<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过<delay8 />我仔细想了一下<tag a="110" b="0" />
<20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听说蟑螂这种生物<delay8 />比我们，
甚至是恐龙还要早<delay20 />
就生活在这个世界上了！<anim id="Shaking" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<20_2 arg="8" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是说，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />它们相当于是<delay8 />
世间种种生物的大前辈对吧？
<20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然如此，<delay8 />敬仰都来不及了，<delay8 />
又怎么能厌恶它们呢？<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />你说对不对？！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然<delay20 />我心里是这么想的，<anim id="Frantic" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />
但到头来，<delay8 />讨厌的东西
还是很讨厌呢<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />怎么样？<delay frames="60" /><anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
这算是一次成功的女生话题吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有一件很在意的事情！<delay40 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一言以蔽之的话，<delay20 />
就是<delay8 /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />“时间旅行的可能性”！
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我呀，<20_3 arg="4" />
特别喜欢读<delay20 /><20_2 arg="8" />
有时光机出现的故事呢！<anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为<delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要乘上时光机，
就有可能遇见恐龙
<20_2 arg="7" />或是未来的自己哦？
<20_3 arg="8" /><anim id="Sleepy" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总有一天，我也想要<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
来一趟时间旅行。<delay8 />
这就是我的愿望！
<anim id="Sleep" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只不过<delay20 /><20_2 arg="3" />除了“现在”之外，
是否还存在其他时间线，<anim id="Eh" target="player" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />
<20_2 arg="4" />仍然是个未知数呢<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然这个问题<delay8 />
百思不得其解，<20_3 arg="7" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我依然<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />怀抱着梦想！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么样？<20_2 arg="3" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />这算是一次成功的女生话题吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有一件非常在意的事情！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一言以蔽之的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是<delay8 />“人鱼是否是真实存在的？”这个问题！
<20_2 arg="8" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />常有人说<delay8 />我们平时听到的传闻，<20_3 arg="4" />
只不过是把海牛错看成了人鱼而已，<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />但我相信人鱼是真实存在的！
<20_2 arg="6" /><anim id="Restless" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望有一天我能够见到人鱼，<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="5" />详细了解一下海中的生活方式，<delay8 />
以及人鱼的历史<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Sleepy" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />然后，<delay8 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" />如果能把这些事情写成一本书，
那就太棒了！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么样？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="60" />
这算是一次成功的女生话题吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样的女生话题，<delay8 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />我从没听过啦！<anim id="WrySmile" target="player" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对不起，<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />是我错了！<anim id="WrySmile" target="player" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我正在找能送给<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的礼物啦，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />可是一直找不到呀～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">选礼物确实是一件有趣的事情，<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过找不到合适的礼物时，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />会令人很不安呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00">那个那个，<20_2 arg="3" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><20_2 arg="8" />
你觉得要怎么样<delay8 /><20_3 arg="3" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才能找到适合的礼物呀？</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">偷偷调查</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">询问本人</message>
	<message label="103_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">送自己喜欢的东西</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～！<delay40 /><20_3 arg="6" />这么一说，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉好像女间谍一样，<delay8 />
感觉超～级帅气的耶！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">女间谍<20_2 arg="2" />是吗<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像是故事里的剧情一样，感觉好棒！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果不嫌弃的话，需不需要我也来帮忙呀？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个<20_2 arg="3" />超赞的～！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那好，<delay20 /><anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我们首先得找两套
一样的<delay8 />间谍装束呢！</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />咦！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />穿成那样的话，<delay8 />
反而会更引人注目吧<anim id="WrySmile" target="player" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嗯～<20_3 arg="6" /><delay40 /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样确实是可以
送到对方想要的东西，<delay20 />
但是就没有惊喜的感觉了<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想到<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="2" />一个好主意了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我直接去问问<delay8 />
对方想要什么吧！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_3 arg="5" />问完之后，<delay20 />我再把答案
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />告诉<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 /><anim id="Aha" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />你们看怎么样？</message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay8 />你好聪明呀！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那可以拜托你吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />问的时候一定要<delay8 />轻～描淡写哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="4" />一定要注意<delay20 />轻～描淡写对吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
我会努力<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />回应你的期待的！<delay8 /><anim id="Clapping" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_3 arg="6" />这样好像<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也可以耶～<delay40 />
要是人家<delay8 />真的不喜欢，
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我还可以拿回来自己用呀！</message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />毕竟<20_2 arg="2" />送礼的这份心意，<delay8 />
<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />才是最重要的呢！</message>
	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay40 />那就送
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最喜欢的偶像的写真集，<delay20 />
还有官方马克杯吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="115" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<20_2 arg="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
但是又感觉送一些<delay8 />
更贴近对方喜好的礼物会比较好<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />
借给我的那本诗集，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />真的超～级棒哦～！
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我自己都能感觉到，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />啊，所谓的磨练感性是这么一回事呀！<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉自己的创作欲都被激发啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<20_2 arg="4" /><delay8 />
能帮上你的忙，<delay20 />真是太好了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得从<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你的口头禅中，<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />
好像也能感受到情绪了！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />真的吗？！<delay frames="60" /><anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
连平时的口头禅都带上了诗意，<delay8 />
我到底是<delay8 />磨练到什么地步啦？
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />……<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是不是也想试一试呀～？<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我完全不介意的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的可以吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么好事不宜迟，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在就来用用看吧！<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />这样一来，<delay8 />
我是不是也能变得像<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />一样，<delay8 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
感性丰富呀？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
